            <p style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.6em;margin: 0;padding: 0;font-weight: normal;margin-bottom: 12px;">When the location of your polling place is official we'll send you an update, and as the election approaches we'll be in touch about transportation to the polls.</p>

            <!-- <h2>How do I use it?</h2> -->
